I don't believe that there's a limit to anything. There's always some way to get around it. Sure, Universal laws are laws, but there are always ways to get around them, or sneak by the interstellar police undetected. As long as you know what you doing, (and as long as your tests dont explode!) there's no "limit" to anything. History has proven this again and again.
